text: Carnegie Hall Tower is a 60-story skyscraper on 57th Street in New York City. The tower is 231 meters (757 ft) tall and was completed in 1991. ==Other websites== * Official site *in-Arch.net: The Carnegie Hall Tower * Carnegie Hall Tower at emporis.com Category:Skyscrapers in New York City Category:1991 establishments in New York (state) Category:Buildings and structures in Manhattan
